\pard\f0\fs28  {\b  P. reuteri} Boiss.,{\i  Diagn. Pl. Or. Nov. }{\b 3}({\b 2}): 51 (1856), from S. Spain, is probably of hybrid origin from {\b 28} and {\b 30}. It is like {\b 28} but the basal leaves have not more than 7(-9) teeth or lobes and the achenes are without a narrow membranous margin.
