\pard\f0\fs28    {\b 33. P. umbrosa} Steven ex Bieb.,{\i  Fl. Taur.-Cauc. }{\b 3}: 357 (1819). Like {\b 32} but leaves digitate with 5 leaflets; sepals ovate, subobtuse; epicalyx-segments oblong-ovate. •{\i  Krym}. Rs (K)
